P. Koutsakis, M. Paterakis and S. Psychis, “Integrating Voice, Video and Bursty Data Packet Traffic Over Burst-Error Wireless TDMA Channels with Adjustable Request Bandwidth”, in Proc. of the 12th IEEE International Symposium on Personal, Indoor and Mobile Radio Communications (PIMRC 2001), October 2001, San Diego, California, pp. G-55 – G-59.